# Rust build artifacts (this sub-workspace builds the wasm component here when
# `--target-dir target` is used; the machine-local .cargo config may redirect it
# elsewhere). Cargo.lock IS committed: a pinned lock keeps the shipped component
# reproducible across CI wheel/wasm builds.
/target/

# jco transpile output and npm.
/dist/
/node_modules/

# Generated guest bindings (regenerated by `cargo component build`).
/src/bindings.rs
